Package: DEMATELSpectral
Type: Package
Title: Spectral Analysis and Sensitivity Analysis Extensions for DEMATEL Method
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Pavlos", "Delias", email = "pdelias@af.duth.gr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Enhances the Decision-Making Trial and Evaluation Laboratory (DEMATEL) 
    method with spectral analysis capabilities and comprehensive sensitivity analysis,
    providing deeper insights into system dynamics, stability characteristics, 
    intervention potential through eigenvalue decomposition, and critical 
    relationship identification through sensitivity matrices.
